22	1000	3	9	Custom hooks and context	TEXT	<h2>Share logic and global state</h2>\n<p>Extract repeated effect logic into <code>useSomething</code> hooks. Use Context for theme, auth, or locale — but avoid putting everything in one giant context.</p>	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	t	2026-05-25 11:28:45.107	\N
23	1000	3	9	Lists, keys, and performance basics	TEXT	<h2>Render collections correctly</h2>\n<p>Stable <code>key</code> props (IDs, not array index) help React reconcile lists. Memoize expensive calculations with <code>useMemo</code> and callbacks with <code>useCallback</code> only when profiling shows a need.</p>	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	1	t	2026-05-25 11:28:45.109	\N
24	1000	3	10	Routing, layouts, and server components	TEXT	<h2>File-system routing in Next.js</h2>\n<p><code>app/dashboard/page.tsx</code> maps to <code>/dashboard</code>. <code>layout.tsx</code> wraps nested routes. Server Components fetch data on the server by default — mark client interactivity with <code>"use client"</code>.</p>	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	t	2026-05-25 11:28:45.115	\N
